==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Submaxillary
<hw>Sub*max"il*la*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>Situated under the maxilla, or lower jaw;
inframaxillary; <as>as, the <ex>submaxillary</ex> gland</as>.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>Of or pertaining to submaxillary gland; <as>as,
<ex>submaxillary</ex> salvia</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Submedial</ent>⟦br⟧
